name: community
topic:
🤝 **__Welcome!__** :handshake: 

As you all may have noticed, we like shouting out big projects within the server community. We love to see people work hard towards stuff and want to do our best to reward that where we can and promote the cool stuff that this community comes up with. To continue to do this in a way that we feel is right, we have added this channel. 

We will mainly be using this as a way to shout out projects and events produced by the community. We will see where it takes us! What gets announced here is entirely up to our admin's discretion, not everything that is big will be announced here. Just the stuff we feel is worthy!

name: support
topic:
A place for you to ask for general help. Questions about game's mechanics, community details and such should be asked in this channel. 

Please keep in mind this is not a place to report bugs, users, or levels. It is also not a place to suggest features for the game or ask for help building things in-game or completing levels.

Inquire about more complex issues related to in-game difficulties, game bugs, and account problems via RobTop's support mail: support@robtopgames.com

name: giveaways
topic:
🎉・In this channel you will find giveaways hosted by our members. You can enter a giveaway by adding a reaction while it is still running.

・Make sure to assign yourself the **Giveaway Notifications** role in <#881709788826837033> if you want to be notified for new giveaways!
Giveaway hosts receive the “Giveaway Patron” role.

・To claim your prize, please send the Giveaway Host a direct message.
